            <h2>Start Your Custom Build Journey</h2>
            <p>Have a question about a specific switch? Or are you ready to commission a full high-end keyboard build? Fill out the form below (simulated) or reach out via email.</p>
            
            <form action="#" method="post" style="max-width: 400px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;">
