                <label for="message">Your Request (e.g., Switch Lubing):</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                
                <button type="submit" style="background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 10px; cursor: pointer;">Send Inquiry</button>
            </form>

            <p>For more information on the history of typing technology, you can visit the <a href="https://www.smithsonianmag.com/tag/typewriters/" target="_blank">Smithsonian Institution</a>.</p>
